org.hps.record.daqconfig

Class DAQConfig

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.hps.record.daqconfig.IDAQConfig
      • org.hps.record.daqconfig.DAQConfig

  • public class DAQConfig
extends IDAQConfig
    Class DAQConfig holds all of the supported parameters from the DAQ configuration that exists in EVIO files. These values are stored in various subclasses appropriate to the parameter that are accessed through this primary interface.
